{"tid":2512054,"cid":34,"subCid":0,"title":"(台測)好似好勁揪系列 4","createTime":"2021-05-01T11:29:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-01T20:49:45.000Z","uid":29160,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"38fd21518456c3749af508314b6418832fc9869d","tid":2512054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:29:32.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\">支肺已經殺到黎 自己注意身體<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span><br />\n<span class=\"xx-large\">睇清楚時間幾點播</span><br />\n<a href=\"http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fparadiseangel.wixsite.com%2Fthanksyour%2Fabout1&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=b82adbef\" target=\"_blank\">http://paradiseangel.wixsite.com/thanksyour/about1</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 關ADBLOCK先睇到V台 順便開返個FLASHPLAYER 無CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Flive.sk-knower.com%2Fuser%2Fthanksyour%3Flive%3Dvl&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=2e159676\" target=\"_blank\">http://live.sk-knower.com/user/thanksyour?live=vl</a> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得返OK台(自己按播放制) 有CHATROOM<br />\n<a href=\"https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.wixstatic.com%2Fmedia%2Fd8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=432e8deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://static.wixstatic.com/media/d8ce1b_739a0b287f954af3860f1f3f8b383a4f~mv2.jpg</a> &lt;&lt; GOOGLE睇唔到解決方法好似係 BY伯爵<br />\n<img src=\"https://onlyhdwallpapers.com/wallpaper/jason-statham-movie-posters-20Pf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fonlyhdwallpapers.com%2Fwallpaper%2Fjason-statham-movie-posters-20Pf.jpg&h=ad922f29&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/f/f3/Accident_Man_Poster.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2Ff%2Ff3%2FAccident_Man_Poster.jpg&h=35320f64&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/zh/3/3d/StevenSeagalUnderSiege_cover.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.wikimedia.org%2Fwikipedia%2Fzh%2F3%2F3d%2FStevenSeagalUnderSiege_cover.jpg&h=fb4bd3af&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n1.職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）為了心愛的未婚妻伊娃（艾咪&middot;史瑪特飾）打算金盆洗手，但是人在江湖飄，哪有不挨刀，就在他想退出江湖時，仇家上門報復，而且是非常特異的手法：在他睡夢中注射一種毒藥，要讓他心臟麻痺而死。契夫在痛苦中求救，終於發現了暫保活命的方法，作極其激烈的運動，讓心臟猛跳，只要心跳一減緩，他就會死。他要如何保住小命，救出被擄走的愛人呢？<br />\n<br />\n2.上一次大難不死的職業殺手契夫（傑森&middot;史塔森飾）又遇到艱辛萬倍的挑戰，有人將他的心臟奪走，改以一個人工幫浦取代，甚至還有一個不知名的華人黑道組織要取他器官，而這次契夫要一直為自己的幫浦心臟充電，否則就會一命不保，所以他竭盡腦汁，用了變電箱、汽車電池、電擊棒，甚至是靜電來維繫生命，究竟他要如何保住性命，追回自己的心臟呢？<br />\n<br />\n3.麥克&middot;福隆（斯科特&middot;阿金斯飾），號稱意外殺手的他，是位冷血殺手。就他從事的職業來講，他是頂尖的，無論是條理多樣的刺殺技巧，還是瞞天過海躲過警察視線，他的每次任務都使雇主滿意高興。但是有一天他摯愛的人卻捲入了倫敦的地下殺手世界，並慘遭自己同組織的人殺害。而福隆不得不打破自己長久以來井然有序，條理安排的生活，開始向實施這一切的人展開復仇<br />\n<br />\n4.美國軍艦密蘇里號即將退役，在返回港口途中遭到前任CIA情報員史傳尼克斯（湯米&middot;李&middot;瓊斯飾演）率領的傭兵劫持，傭兵一夥人和副艦長奎爾裡應外合欲將載有核彈頭的戰斧巡弋飛彈賣給軍火販子，但他們沒想到艦上大廚雷白克（史蒂芬&middot;席格飾演）原本是海軍海豹特勤隊的成員，並精通功夫、爆破等作戰技能...........<br />\n<br />\n8 30PM左右播了 隨時電腦大爆炸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Faddons.mozilla.org%2Fen-US%2Ffirefox%2Faddon%2Fghostery%2F&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=5dfb96e3\" target=\"_blank\">https://addons.mozilla.org/en-US/firefox/addon/ghostery/</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchrome.google.com%2Fwebstore%2Fdetail%2Fghostery%2Fmlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij%3Fhl%3Dzh-TW&d=Z1ElB6oaYTZYlgUQOIdQNiUaeeTarj8%2BpjPG%2B7PQGFg%3D&h=ebc2ec5e\" target=\"_blank\">https://chrome.google.com/webstore/detail/ghostery/mlomiejdfkolichcflejclcbmpeaniij?hl=zh-TW</a><br />\n裝左睇V台就唔會見左上果舊野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/slick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35b753ec16538fcf693ca7ebfcf03d4c4d0d8c8a","tid":2512054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T11:30:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16ee9b9c2fd770749291b8dbb7b721f78b274101","tid":2512054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T13:38:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/potion.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9431268f81fcee1dc288d06e85d275c8bba435","tid":2512054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T14:09:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a237ee66196661ed03b2028068d4906fdc13b476","tid":2512054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T17:30:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/FBI.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7fc7cd7ce8b4bb49c170ea4676be10c45c1ebd3f","tid":2512054,"uid":29160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-01T20:49:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}